            <p>Michigan&nbsp;does&nbsp;offer online voter registration but for updates only&nbsp;<strong>NOT first time registration.</strong>&nbsp;</p>

<p>For information on how to register to vote or update your registration, visit the state's voter registration information webpage:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.michigan.gov/sos/0,1607,7-127-1633_8716_8726_47669-175878--,00.html" target="_blank">https://www.michigan.gov/sos/0,1607,7-127-1633_8716_8726_47669-175878--,00.html​</a>.</p>

