<table>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<th>Registration Deadline</th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>15 days before Election Day by mail and online*</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>*In Michigan, you can also register in-person at any time up to 8 p.m. on Election Day at your city or township clerk’s office.</p>

<p><em>Updated on November 12, 2024.</em></p>

